<div class="banner w-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
  <h1>This revolution doesn't need a guillotine.</h1>
  <h2>Improve your city with a simple alert!</h2>
  <%= link_to "Send an alert", pages_path, class: "fs-5 fw-bold btn btn-primary rounded-pill" %>
</div>
<div class="container">

  <div class="map-container d-flex justify-content-center mt-5">
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 400px;"
    data-controller="map"
    data-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
    data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>"></div>
  </div>
  <h2 class="text-center my-4">About</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="cards d-flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-content-between">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 d-flex flex-column align-items-center mx-2">
        <div class="homepage-card d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width: 300px">
          <%= image_tag "globe.png", width: 80, height: 80 %>
          <h4 class="fw-bold mt-3">What is Ouicity?</h4>
          <p>We want to bring the joy back to city living! Even though we're all living amongst each other, we
          can still feel at home. Part of being home is working together to keep it beautiful. Our app gets you directly
          involved in your cityâ€™s well-being.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 d-flex flex-column align-items-center mx-2">
        <div class="homepage-card d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width: 300px">
          <%= image_tag "globe.png", width: 80, height: 80 %>
          <h4 class="fw-bold mt-3">Why use it?</h4>
          <p>To make your voice heard! Sick of seeing cars parked in the bike lane you use to commute? Let us know!
          We
        the app simplifies the process and puts you in direct contact with your
          city officials. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-3 d-flex flex-column align-items-center mx-2">
        <div class="homepage-card d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width: 300px">
          <%= image_tag "globe.png", width: 80, height: 80 %>
          <h4 class="fw-bold mt-3">How does it work?</h4>
          <p>You can identify a specific location where you will then be asked to create an
          alert. Once created, your city team will take care of the rest! Sit back and relax! And,
          of course, the city team will let you know once they've solved your alert.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="form-container d-flex flex-column align-items-center text-center">
    <h2 class="text-center my-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <%= form_for @contact, class: "d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center" do |f| %>
        <%= f.text_field  :name, required: true,
                          class: "form-control bg-white",
                          placeholder: "Name" %></br>
        <%= f.text_field :email, required: true,
                         class: "form-control bg-white",
                         placeholder: "Email" %></br>
        <%= f.text_area :message, rows: 8, cols: 40, required: true, class: "form-control bg-white",
              placeholder: "Tell us what's up!"%></br>

          <div class= "d-none">
            <%= f.label :nickname %>
            <%= f.text_field :nickname, :hint => 'Leave this field blank!' %>
          </div>

        <%= f.submit 'Send Message', class: 'text-white btn btn-primary rounded-4' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>
